&lt;http://www.esnips.com/doc/a6873d89-244c-42a5-94f7-cc3534ae72c7/WE-ARE-SEVEN
&gt;  ARE SEVEN) and so I asked what Seven meant to them..  Here is the reply I
got which I gotta admit was pretty cool:



WITH
&lt;http://www.esnips.com/doc/f8c977df-d425-44ac-939b-4b3f5c1b2b9e/WITH-CHRIST-
